Title: 1987 Hamer Chapparal with Dragonskin Finish by Jim O'Connor
Body (HTML): Hamer Chapparal in one of a kind Dragonskin Finish by Jim O'Connor. S/S/H pickup configuration with set neck and Boomerrang inlays. Floyd Rose Tremolo. Some wear on back but no breaks or repairs and is in original condition. Comes with Trem arm and original Hamer hardshell case. Serial #718285

Title: 1987 Mosrite JM 65 Double Neck Joe Maphis Model
Body (HTML):
1987 Mosrite Joe Maphis JM 65 in excellent original condition. Very low production and is complete with original case and letters of provenance from Semie Moseley and Gruhn Guitars. Any questions please ask and we will be more than happy to get back to you.

Year: 1987
Serial # JM 16
Body and Neck: Maple w/walnut laminate
Fingerboard: Rosewood
Weight: 11 lbs
Short 6 string octave neck & standard length 6 string neck. 
All hardware and electronics original.
